data.description: Wonderfully maintained stucco home on a little over an acre of land that backs to open space. Enjoy views of the Front Range, Sangre de Cristo Mountains, and Pikes Peak from every angle of the property. There is over 1800+ sq ft of living space with an open floor plan, ceiling fans, vaulted ceilings and main level master suite with adjoining bath. As you enter the home you are greeted to a spacious living room with large picture window. The kitchen/dining area has stainless steel appliances and walks out to the fully fenced backyard and covered patio. The main level master suite has a full attached bath with generous countertops and a 2nd main level bathroom. The basement features a family room, bathroom, 2 more bedrooms, laundry and storage room. Outside offers RV parking, and oversized/attached 2 car garage, a covered front patio, play set, and separate workshop with electricity.
